{"tid":953528,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蟢茶在港首間分店開幕 早上300人排隊","createTime":"2018-12-24T04:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T04:20:55.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c47c06ac9de41911de2cbf33fba7ca2bd9559a01","tid":953528,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:12:10.000Z","msg":"內地品牌「喜茶HEYTEA」在香港開設的首間分店，今日於沙田新城市廣場開幕，早上10時開幕前，已有約300人店外排隊等候，人龍幾近企滿整個樓層。喜茶貼出告示，首3日有買一送一優惠，但因為購買人數眾多，每人只購2杯。排隊等開門的大多數是年輕人，有排顧客稱早在開店前一個半小時已到達。<br />\n<br />\n在內地爆紅的「喜茶」今年在上海、北京開店時，出現超長人龍，排隊數小時才買到飲品；有內地媒體質疑該店在上海開業首天排隊的300多人疑似「造媒」，「喜茶」當時極力否認。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181224/59064586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59064586&d=BOTFg90aRdpsR6jSq54p9gEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=6fbbf66b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59064586&h=6c2b4744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181224/59064586</a>"},{"pid":"9742b63020d5e6837044c5f9fd1e8fa4ef9f5a20","tid":953528,"uid":107364,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"312b642344483038d7d09e94bae1e61b84f98eae","tid":953528,"uid":89383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9742b63020d5e6837044c5f9fd1e8fa4ef9f5a20","tid":953528,"uid":107364,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afd048d4c1bc52eb87032cbc8320d07d96f07b0","tid":953528,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-